2. Calls `wheel.insert(entry)` to add to the timing wheel
3. Stores the expiration time in `TimerShared::state`
4. If the new timer is sooner than `next_wake`, calls `unpark()` to wake the driver thread

**File: `/home/bench/repos/tokio/tokio/src/runtime/time/entry.rs` (lines 142-149)**

